name: Yes, this is the Doge’s Palace
description: Not gonna lie, this REALLY IS the Doge’s Palace in Piazza di San Marco, Venice. You just have to focus hard and use your imagination to see the beauty of the place through this photo-based image taken there at night. Follow me for more like this @fotokopid, alternatively book yourself a trip there and see it for yourself. You won’t regret it!
